From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


This is a maintenance category, used for maintenance of the Wikipedia project. It is not part of the encyclopedia and contains non-article pages, or groups articles by status rather than subject. Do not include this category in content categories.
This category is used for maintaining the template namespace.  No templates should appear directly in this category. This page is part of Wikipedia's administration and not part of the encyclopedia.
For a category of templates themselves, see Category:Wikipedia templates.
This category is for Wikipedia project pages related to templates.
